features: 【Large Capacity Utensil Holder】If you don’t have a lot of drawer space to storge your kitchen utensils, I think this Kitchen Utensil Holder will suit for you. Our large Kitchen Utensil Caddy size is 11.8"Lx4.7"Wx6.7"H, provides plenty of room for all your cookware or cutlery. This rectangular wood Utensil Organizer Box take up minimal countertop space and can be used for a dining table, dining room, patio, or wherever tabletop needed.

【Kitchen Essential Storage Organizer Box】Our farmhouse Utensil Storage Holder made of 100% premium solid pine wood is more sturdy and durable, 3 compartments designed easy to store various cookware, knives, spatulas, tongs, egg beaters, ladle, Skimmers, peelers, corkscrews, silverware, forks, chopsticks and more, keep your kitchen utensils neatly in place. ***Note: The package is not include any tableware！！！

【Thoughtful Wall Hanging and Drainage Design】This kitchen utensils organizer is designed with two wall hooks on the back, so you can also mount it on the wall to store kitchen cutlery and silverware. We also designed multiple drainage holes at the bottom which you can put the freshly cleaned cutlery directly into the cutlery organizer without worrying about the problem of draining water. Thoughtful design only saves you more time.

【Rustic Farmhouse Kitchen Decor】This Flatware Organizer matches nicely with the style of most kitchens, offering a cozy, rustic flair that anyone would definitely love! This farmhouse Utensil Crock with smooth hand feel and original wood texture adds vintage vibe to your kitchen which is the perfect decorative touch to your kitchen countertop.

【Ideal Gift Choice】When you or your friends are troubled by messy kitchen utensils nowhere to put, I think anyone who likes a well-organized kitchen will not refuse this beautiful present. Give it to your loved ones,friends,colleague for Housewarming Parties, Mother’s Day or any other special day and rest assured that you will be remembered for your choice!

reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this thing. It looks great on my kitchen counter and is the perfect size for storing all of my utensils. The wooden finish looks really modern and matches my kitchen décor perfectly. The three compartments are a great way to keep my utensils organized and easy to find. I would definitely recommend this utensil holder to anyone looking for a stylish and functional way to store their kitchen utensils.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love it!
reviews.reviewText: It looks so nice and holds a lot! It helped free up tons of space in my cooking utensil drawer so now it’s not overflowing and getting caught every time I open it. It also takes up way less space on my counter then my old round one, by sitting flat against the wall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Super cute and decent size, but paint is not sealed.
reviews.reviewText: Got this for my birthday. It is super cute! And fits on my counter perfectly. It holds all of my cooking utensils with room to spare, but it doesn’t take up a lot of space on the counter. My only complaint, is that the paint in not sealed. As I was cleaning it before I put my stuff in it, I noticed some sawdust and black paint on the rag. I plan on sealing it myself so that the paint lasts longer and doesn’t continue to wipe off anytime I have to clean it.
